{
  "texts": [
    "There are two types of improvements to achieve this goal.",
    "The first improvement is replacing the DNN with RNN.",
    "By this mean, the temporal features of each wind turbine are first extracted by the RNN, and the spatial-temporal features are finally provided by the GNN.",
    "The second improvement is to reorganize the input z as a time series.",
    "In each time step, the GNN is used to extract the spatial feature."
  ]
}